{
    "name": "Fatal Axe",
    "type": "npc",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Tactics",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>Before Combat </b>The assassin uses Stealth or Disguise to get close to her prey so she can study and strike with her death attack.<br/><b>During Combat </b>Using her fast stealth and <i>boots of speed </i>to rush into the fray, the assassin attacks the most threatening target using bleeding strike. Next, she moves out of melee to soften foes with throwing axe attacks before reentering melee."
        },
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "html": "Surprisingly quick and nimble for dwarves, fatal axes mix melee prowess with devastating throwing axe strikes to bring down their foes."
        }
    ],
